Client: Commonwealth of technology, Frankfort KY
May,2019-Tilldate Role: Sr UI/UX Designer (Salesforces)
Kumar.tangella@ky.gov
Salesforces trailhead : https://trailhead.salesforce.com/en/me/stangella3
Tools and Technologies Used:

HTML, CSS3, JavaScript, jQuery, TypeScript, Eclipse, Ajax, DOM, Bit Bucket, Salesforce, Lightning Components, Lightning web Components, wireframes, prototypes, Mockup

Descriptions:
Project 1:

ABC project is about Kentucky Alcohol beverage control which is a licensing portal for applying for licenses for alcohol sales and production in this project we are working on building an online portal where citizens and public can go and apply for the licenses in order to do the business legally. In this process the user can apply for new applications and renewal of applications additional requests that are needed to run their business.

Project 2:

Grands managements project is about Kentucky Project Funding which is a Application portal for applying for Project fundingâ€™s and production in this project we are working on building an online portal where Kentucky Government having different Cabinets can go and apply for the project funds. In this process the user can apply for new project funds

Responsibilities:

- As a UX designer, I partnered with designers to work through the early stages of a design or product working from strategy and feature definition into Flow charts, sketching and prototyping, and iterating.
- Adjusted current wireframes to reflect UI/ UX standards.
- Redesigned the interfaces according to established style guide.
- Rendering with Sketchup, Photoshop, and Illustrator.
- Have delivered Multiple successful live products for Android, Ios and web platforms.
- Developed the User Interface with HTML, HTML5, CSS, CSS3, JavaScript,ES6, Bootstrap.
- Used ES6 and JSX with react for component development. Used Babel to compile JSX and Es6 into JavaScript.
- Involved in creating, monitoring, and measuring campaigns with Salesforce CRM Marketing.
- Administered Salesforce.com applications and migrated code/data from different environments.
- Customized page layouts for Salesforce.com standard and custom objects.
- Proficient in using VScode based Salesforce.com IDE to develop and deploy force.com software.
- Created multiple Lightning Components, added CSS and Design Parameters that makes the Lightning component look and feel better.
- Lightning web components are custom HTML elements built using HTML and modern JavaScript.
